summary: This is an email exchange regarding an annual evidence inventory check for the NYPD/FBI Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force. An FBI Office Services Supervisor requests confirmation of possession for several evidence items with specific case numbers.

events.title: Annual Evidence Inventory
events.description: The NYPD/FBI Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force is conducting its annual evidence inventory, requesting confirmation of possession for specific evidence items.

locations: New York Field Office, Federal Bureau of Investigation
keyFacts: The communication is related to the NYPD/FBI Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force.
Several evidence items with case numbers (e.g., 305D-NY-2944995, 50D-NY-3027571) are listed for inventory confirmation.
The email is external and dated August 12, 2020, regarding an inventory due by the end of that week.
The sender is identified as an Office Services Supervisor (OSS) at the FBI's New York Field Office.
The document reference EFTA00146695 is noted as a desk identifier.
